{"tid":1066852,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"求鬚刨推介","createTime":"2019-03-18T07:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T13:52:52.000Z","uid":187286,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec70efe2ecfac6e039e2f512ca1eebf610e82c6","tid":1066852,"uid":187286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"想買個鬚刨比男朋友<br />\n但市面上有好多唔同設計，價位又好唔同<br />\n睇過有巴打話買Barun牌9系就無敵<br />\n但岩岩落豐澤問，個sales又叫我揀Philips因為佢係3個旋轉頭無咁傷面<br />\n事關我男朋友用開剃鬚刀，成日剃到塊面傷哂紅哂變生瘡<br />\n所以今次想買個好d嘅鬚刨比佢<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係好多鬚，係d皮膚易紅易敏感易傷<br />\n求各位推介應該買咩款／咩設計<br />\nBudget無咩所謂<br />\n最緊要好用"},{"pid":"a3aa1550a6f86939864e136463f92bfb68434aae","tid":1066852,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"Miniso 電動鬚刨"},{"pid":"f33a052c071012515b17ac734975538014fc535a","tid":1066852,"uid":212943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"認真我都想知"},{"pid":"cde2d654b67f1cb57ad71433b0e24c3058c08bd1","tid":1066852,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"咁呢個係佢皮膚問題喎 <br />\n唔關鬚刨事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵下用邊隻鬚後水好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5a49ea7dfc406635202ee79ecbaec1001366c6","tid":1066852,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"Barun9系水貨"},{"pid":"f5f78552e0061b6c4ecbd0307f44e72324cde2d7","tid":1066852,"uid":187286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cde2d654b67f1cb57ad71433b0e24c3058c08bd1","tid":1066852,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"咁呢個係佢皮膚問題喎 <br />\n唔關鬚刨事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵下用邊隻鬚後水好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass